org.apache.hc.core5.http.nio

Class AsyncClientEndpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hc.core5.http.nio.AsyncClientEndpoint

  • @Contract(threading=SAFE)
public abstract class AsyncClientEndpoint
extends Object
    Client endpoint leased from a connection manager.

    Once the endpoint is no longer needed it MUST be released with releaseAndReuse() or releaseAndDiscard().

    Since:
    5.0
